channel.title: Delta Scape Question
channel.description:
When I added a Portal and made it so when you clicked it it teleported you to the TzHaar caves but when I clicked it turned to level 51 wild at edge and said the welcoming message. When I logged back in I was at level 51 wild.
Picture:
[IMG]http://i263.photobucket.com/albums/ii150/360236/untitled-10.jpg[/img]
Portal Code:
[code]makeGlobalObject(3091, 3506, 7272, 0, 10);[/code]
Case Code(To Teleport them to): [code] case 7272: absX = 3153; absY = 3923; sM("Welcome To The TzHaar Caves!"); break;[/code]
I know why it was at 51 wild(Cords) but why did it not tele me there?

item.title: Delta Scape Question
item.description:
@360236 wrote:

Fixed:

case 7272: toX = 3153; toY = 3923; sM("Welcome To The TzHaar Caves!"); break;

Thank you.
